name: Egg on Cat 2
description:
This is a collaboration project between HiyokoNFT (Tamago-Kake Association) and LunaSui.



Egg on Cat

It was one morning. As the cat was walking, suddenly something cold fell on his head.
“Ew! What is this!?” The cat squeaked in surprise.

“It is an egg!” A very happy voice came from behind. The cat looked up and saw a chicken standing there with an egg on his head. The chicken continues to speak confidently. "I'm the president of the Tamago-Kake Association. I have judged you worthy of putting an egg on top of. See, you're just like me!"

As the chicken eloquently explained the appeal of eggs, the cat's mind was gradually dyed with the color of eggs.
